title: Wall Street firms see Fed tapering bond buys starting next year

title: Stock Market Today: Stocks Tiptoe Forward as Stimulus Talks Persist

Despite these negative headlines, the SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust (NYSE: SPY) continues to rally, leaving some investors to wonder why the market is seemingly ignoring the news cycle.
